snippet.title: Aquametsis | Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
The infiltration demo is now available on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2696550/Aquametsis/

Aquametsis, a unique fusion of Immersive Sim, Tactical FPS, and Strategy set in a submerged corporate hellscape. Command mercenaries on infiltration missions, engage in tactical combat, and manage your private mercenary company.

#fps #indiegame #immersivesim #strategy #gamedev
